ike this one are going to happen in the near future if nothing is done to stop police brutality. Thanks a lot for your time!<br />\n<br />\nA group of concerned Hong Kongers"},{"pid":"44a18761bef37f53b37dea02a8c450ecd346a7b0","tid":1408874,"uid":271627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69dd117ccb9cb53bab8eaf5d2319eb6f3ce5094b","tid":1408874,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:18:32.000Z","msg":"Chung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰<br />\n18 分鐘 &middot; <br />\n有無人知天水圍女仔全名？<br />\n請PM我。<br />\n我就到現場，律師後到與我會合。<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳，一定要全名，否則跟唔到。<br />\n<br />\n松泰係現場喇.求大家幫幫手搵女仔名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4abb58410f1f5d0473ce06d5c6f22614aa411df1","tid":1408874,"uid":271627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44a18761bef37f53b37dea02a8c450ecd346a7b0","tid":1408874,"uid":271627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"69dd117ccb9cb53bab8eaf5d2319eb6f3ce5094b","tid":1408874,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:18:32.000Z","msg":"Chung-Tai Cheng 鄭松泰<br />\n18 分鐘 &middot; <br />\n有無人知天水圍女仔全名？<br />\n請PM我。<br />\n我就到現場，律師後到與我會合。<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳，一定要全名，否則跟唔到。<br />\n<br />\n松泰係現場喇.求大家幫幫手搵女仔名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:20:46.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T19:23:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2af631c05622d8ca6a5d8734238e924772920293","tid":1408874,"uid":293036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote